    },
    {
      "key": "fc0d5ae8-27fb-42f9-a868-5bc95906e5ac",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Discuss:** *This code segment is supposed to swap the values in variables `firstNumber` and `secondNumber`, but it has an error. What do we need to add, remove, or change to correct this code segment?*\n\n**Discussion Goal:** Students suggest adding a temporary variable to perform the swap. The value stored in `firstNumber` should be copied to the temporary variable. The value stored in `secondNumber` can then be copied to the `firstNumber` variable, and then the value stored in the temporary variable can be copied to the `secondNumber` variable.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Review the concepts covered in this lesson.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Review the Question of the Day.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Display:** Key Vocabulary",
        "name": "Swapping Values"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "fc0d5ae8-27fb-42f9-a868-5bc95906e5ac",
        "lesson_activity.key": "e9ade4fc-4231-4633-ba84-c52932dde7a5"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "b994e224-03fd-48aa-b136-fc880f6d1896",
      "position": 2,
      "properties": {
        "description": "---"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "b994e224-03fd-48aa-b136-fc880f6d1896",
        "lesson_activity.key": "e9ade4fc-4231-4633-ba84-c52932dde7a5"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "962c9a48-28da-4776-8369-ca7b825a881d",
      "position": 3,
      "properties": {
        "description": "*Check For Understanding Question(s) and solutions can be found in each lesson on Code Studio. These questions can be used for an exit ticket.*",
        "name": "Assessment: Check for Understanding",
        "progression_name": "Check for Understanding"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "962c9a48-28da-4776-8369-ca7b825a881d",
