    {
      "key": "f499c801-8311-455d-9df5-bf07e39c382f",
      "position": 4,
      "properties": {
        "description": "You will finish developing your program to create your asphalt art. Be sure to consider the feedback you received from your code review as you work on your program. First, let's revisit the Asphalt Art Project Planning Guide to make sure you have included everything you need to meet the project requirements.",
