      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Direct students to Level 1 on Code Studio to finish developing their Asphalt Art Project. Have students submit their projects at the end of the allotted time."
